fields.name: EndAzimuthDegrees
fields.description: Azimuth of the antenna at the end of the contact in decimal degrees.

fields.name: EndElevationDegrees
fields.description: Spacecraft elevation above the horizon at contact end.

fields.name: MaximumElevationDegrees
fields.description: Maximum elevation of the antenna during the contact in decimal degrees.

fields.name: RxEndTime
fields.description: Time to lost receiving a signal (ISO 8601 UTC standard).

fields.name: RxStartTime
fields.description: Earliest time to receive a signal (ISO 8601 UTC standard).

fields.name: StartAzimuthDegrees
fields.description: Azimuth of the antenna at the start of the contact in decimal degrees.

fields.name: StartElevationDegrees
fields.description: Spacecraft elevation above the horizon at contact start.

fields.name: TxEndTime
fields.description: Time at which antenna transmit will be disabled (ISO 8601 UTC standard).

fields.name: TxStartTime
fields.description: Time at which antenna transmit will be enabled (ISO 8601 UTC standard).
